#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Welcome to &minuet;: the software for music education. &minuet; aims at "
"supporting students and teachers in many aspects of music education, such as "
"ear training, first-sight reading, solfa, scales, rhythm, harmony, and "
"improvisation. &minuet; makes extensive use of &MIDI; capabilities to "
"provide a full-fledged set of features regarding volume, tempo, and pitch "
"changes, which makes &minuet; a valuable tool for both novice and "
"experienced musicians."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&minuet; features a rich set of ear training's exercises and new ones can be "
"<link linkend=\"creating-exercises\"> seamlessly added</link> in order to "
"extend its functionalities and adapt it to several music education contexts."
msgstr ""

